Maintainer: Peter Meissner <retep.meissner@gmail.com>
SystemRequirements: Java
Description: Provides R bindings via 'rJava' for Kafka a big data technology. 
  Kafka is a event log data base to which messages can be published or read 
  from topics. It is distributed, highly scalable, provides persistent event storage 
  and is designed for high throughput.
